title: Ace the Technical Pilot Interview
description:
Hi all,

this is my first torrent. I bought the eBook, opened it with Adobe Digital Editions, printed it as a Microsoft XPS Document Writer, opened the .xps file with Adobe Acrobat 8 Professional, saved it as .pdf, and got this file.

It is a compilation of images of the pages of the book and in spite of their quality is good, the text cannot be selectable nor copied.

If anyone knows a way to convert the eBook file (it is a .pdf) to a pdf with selectable text, just let me know.

Cheers.
